Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.10,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}おはよう世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:39.32,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp0}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.81,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何れ程　歩いたろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:56.78,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}足の痛みだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:59.88,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}その距離を物語る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:06.97,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}長い夜を越えた絶景への期待が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:10.14,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今日　僕を生かしている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:16.06,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神々の霊峰　新緑の宮殿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:21.09,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岩窟の最奥　蒼穹の涯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:26.91,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}踏破してみせる　限界は無い
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:30.20,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}惑星の隅々まで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:33.86,op-jp,,0,0,2,,{\blur2}おはよう世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:37.10,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fsp0\blur2\pos(640,-4)}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:41.12,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不可能の闇を祓って
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:46.50,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神話を日常に変えていく{\fsp0}Odyssey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:55.70,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一歩ずつ石を穿つ様な　この歩みで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:05:00.63,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}世界を拡げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:02.63,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.10,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早安 世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:39.32,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp0}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.81,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我脚步不停
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:56.78,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有双脚的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:59.88,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}知晓走过的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:06.97,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我期待着漫漫长夜后的绝美风景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:10.14,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}活在今天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:16.06,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神之灵峰 新绿宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:21.09,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岩窟深处 苍穹尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:26.91,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都要一一到达 永无止境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:30.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要走遍每一个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:33.86,op-cn,,0,0,2,,{\blur2}早安 世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:37.10,op-cn,,0,0,2,,{\blur2\fsp0}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:41.12,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}驱散名为不可能的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:46.50,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将神话变为日常的{\fsp0}Odyssey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:55.70,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一步又一步 如滴水穿石般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:05:00.63,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拓宽眼前的世界
